org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.rmnode

Class RMDeployingNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.rmnode.AbstractRMNode
      • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.rmnode.RMDeployingNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<RMNode>, RMNode

    public final class RMDeployingNode
extends AbstractRMNode
    This class stands for a node whose deployment has already been launched whereas the RMNode has not been acquired by the RMCore yet. This is purely informative.
    See Also:
